  "title": "Hooklift Truck Driver",
  "description": "<p>Job Description & Requirements</p><p>Responsibilities:</p><p>· Collection of Waste using open-top container and compactor.</p><p>· Filling in service/ delivery order forms as per request.</p><p>· Performing and recording minor maintenance tasks such as greasing, fluid top-ups, etc.</p><p>· Washing the truck and cleaning the interior.<br /></p><p>Requirements:</p><p>·Hold a Class 4/ 5 driving license is a must.</p><p>· Have a minimum of 2-5 years of experience in driving Heavy vehicles with a semi-auto transmission.</p><p>· Have experience in operating a Hooklift Truck.</p><p>· Have a professional attitude towards truck driving.</p><p>· Have a strong focus on customer satisfaction.</p><p>· Prefer to have WSQ Operate Waste Collection Vehicle to Collect Waste (PI-WM-106E-1).</p><p>· Be reliable, punctual, and motivated with a strong work ethic.</p>",
